Banglore me bhi saath me machane wale hain ab....tu trell me jaay ya fk me wapas se...aana banglore hi hoga...plis...
Bhai yaad hai placements me bhi jab meri 24*7 fati rhti thi tab tu hamesha positive sochta tha...tujhe pata hai ki tu kuch na kuch dhang ka to karhi lega....Ye nature same rakhna bro, me kaafi inspired rhta hun teri company me...itna unconventional path choose karke success wali stories me best story teri hi hogi bro...baaki cheezon pe instant reaction dene wali aadat me chudwa dunga teri...
Saath me hi apne aap ko and startup ko grow karenge 
Chal ab emotional baat kaafi ho gyin...kuch bakchodi ki baaten karte hain....if anyone is reading this memoir jaanlo is aadmi ko jo na sirf >10 bandiyon ka kata hai but  kaafi companies ka bhi kaat chuka hai
